{"id":"guide/i18n-optional-overview","title":"可选的国际化实践","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"optional-internationalization-practices\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6m03646fzfy2jynmdq53r3etf\">可选的国际化实践<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-overview#optional-internationalization-practices\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"b2gtlp9015gcx4la1lno9jmbl\">以下可选主题可帮助你手动配置应用程序的国际化设置。可选实践适用于高级或自定义 Angular 应用程序。</p>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e44b21uig1fakj5vcfuvz1bdu\">前提条件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-overview#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2vwgfyttxbb5i4tqwwfwv9zea\">要准备翻译项目，你应该对以下主题有基本的了解。</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"52nvnkmh4saprg8vamomnwca1\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\" title=\"template - Glossary | Angular\">模板</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"vaetn8gsmwrpj42ci4hqh18y\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#component\" title=\"component - Glossary | Angular\">组件</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1r1jmjyx0gbtudese178lmo75\"><a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> <a href=\"guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\" title=\"command-line interface (CLI) - Glossary | Angular\">命令行</a>，管理 Angular 开发周期的工具</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"db650j48xko27f6o1xuqp3v8h\"><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/XML\" title=\"Extensible Markup Language (XML) | W3C\">Extensible Markup Language (XML)</a> 用于翻译文件</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"learn-about-optional-angular-inte